    "analysis": "From the file summaries returned: metric, trace, log, and error_logs all cover the incident window 2022-03-21 04:30–04:59 (UTC+8). Error logs show repeated frontend warnings: 'failed to retrieve ads' starting at 04:30:07 and continuing. Traces/metrics show activity for adservice and frontend pods. This suggests the failure path likely involves frontend → adservice. To follow the prescribed workflow, we must now preprocess metric KPIs for candidate components (frontend and adservice) and compute global thresholds (e.g., P95) for each component-KPI using their full available series in metric.csv before filtering to the incident window. These thresholds will be used to detect anomalies during the incident window. We should keep the output bounded and return only the most informative component-KPI groups.",
